Feeling so grateful to have been a part of @fifpro’s Women’s Football Summit last week in Amsterdam. I had the incredible opportunity to present with @beccaroux about the @uswntplayers journey to equal pay. Meeting other players and learning about their experiences was such a privilege. And a huge bonus attending the UWCL final in Eindhoven! Thank you to everyone involved for such an inspiring few days✨✨
